## Maintenance

Use `hiivmind-corpus` skills to maintain this corpus:

| Command | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `/hiivmind-corpus refresh {{project_name}}` | Update from upstream changes |
| `/hiivmind-corpus enhance {{project_name}} <topic>` | Add depth to a topic |
| `/hiivmind-corpus build {{project_name}}` | Full rebuild |
| `/hiivmind-corpus add-source {{project_name}} <url>` | Add new source |

## config.yaml Schema

```yaml
schema_version: 2

corpus:
  name: "{{project_name}}"
  display_name: "{{project_display_name}}"
  keywords:            # For automatic routing
{{#keywords}}
    - {{.}}
{{/keywords}}

sources:
  - id: {{project_name}}
    type: git
    repo_url: https://github.com/...
    branch: main
    last_commit_sha: "..."
    last_indexed_at: "..."
```

